Yes, it is missing some new files that have been added to the unix  
Makefiles but not to the Windows build procedure.  The files affected  
are those in the Cantera/python directory.  The best thing to do is to  
delete them and re-check them out specifying a date of about a week or  
so.

Clearly, we need to come up with some system that separates the stable  
version in CVS from the development version.

Dave
